# Cargo build artifacts (multi-GB; never committed).
target/

# Cargo's lockfile is intentionally NOT ignored — pinning it ensures
# reproducible iOS builds across machines and across the rosenpass git
# rev we depend on. (Library crates often gitignore Cargo.lock; we treat
# this crate as application-shaped because the iOS app is the consumer.)

